import React from 'react'
import {AppBar, Typography, Toolbar, Box, Button} from '@mui/material'

const Header = () => {
  return (
    <AppBar sx={{background: "#1f1612"}}>
        <Toolbar>
            <Typography variant='h4'>Blogg</Typography>
            <Box>
                <Button>Login</Button>
                <Button>Signup</Button>
            </Box>
        </Toolbar>
    </AppBar>
  )
}

export default Header
